Title: Excel Quick Start

Learn how to create a workbook, enter data, save your workbook to OneDrive, automatically fill a column with Flash Fill, quickly calculate with AutoSum, create a chart, or use conditional formatting with Quick Analysis, freeze the top row, share your workbook to collaborate with others, and set up your mobile apps.
